Hi Bob,

The thread into the case is M9 on 1.8's and 2L, but the other end of  
the stud is threaded as M8.

It makes for a rare and expensive stud, though Richard Atwell has  
located an affordable alternative source if you're ordering a minimum  
of 10 pieces.




